      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/28/1/288/4",
      "text": [
        ": قال أمير المؤمنين صلوات الله عليه للحسن ابنه عليه السلام: يا بني ما المروءة؟ فقال: العفاف وإصلاح المال."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.basel-kadem": [
          "4.\tWith this chain of narrators, from Ahmad bin Muhammed, from some of our companions, that he ascribed it to Sa’d bin Turaif, from Asbagh bin Nubata, from Harith, the half-blinded, that he said: The Commander of the Believers, Allah’s blessings be upon him, said to Hasan, his son, peace be upon him: O my son, what is manliness? He said: Chasteness and rectification of property."
        ]
      }
    },
